front.title: •3B3-888
front.gametext: Once per turn may use 1 Force to target an opponent's character present; target is defense value -3 for remainder of turn. While with another battle droid at a site, draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise.
front.lore: Infantry battle droid belonging to the squad that captured Jar Jar Binks and Captain Tarpals at the Naboo battle plains.
